headline: Donostia Throughout History
text: The best way of adapting to a new country and a new culture is learning about it's most important events. In this sample timeline we are going to cover some of the most important events of Donostia's history and explain their relevance to the city's culture

headline: Medieval and Early Historry
text: To know about the beginings of Donostia, we have to turn back to 12th Century, the time where the city was founded

headline: Foundation of the City
text: San Sebasti√°n was officially founded by King Sancho VI of Navarre. It was granted a fuero (municipal charter) to attract settlers and develop trade.

headline: Incorporation into Castile
text: The city, along with the province of Gipuzkoa, was annexed by the Kingdom of Castile, shifting its allegiance from Navarre.
